OL,3,CPlea for heart valve donors after dip
OL,4,Cin donations
OL,6,FThe NHS has made a plea for heart
OL,7,Fvalve donors after seeing a dip in the
OL,8,Fnumber donated for life-saving
OL,9,Fsurgeries.
OL,11,FThe NHS could not supply around one in
OL,12,Ffive (20%) of heart valve requests
OL,13,Ffrom hospitals last year, according to
OL,14,Fnew figures from NHS Blood and
OL,15,FTransplant.
OL,17,FThis comes after a dip in the number
OL,18,Fof hearts donated to heart valve
OL,19,Fbanks, with 600 hearts donated in 2021
OL,20,Fand just 368 donated in 2024.
