OL,3,CPlea for heart valve donors after dip
OL,4,Cin donations
OL,6,FIt is calling on people to support
OL,7,Ftissue donation on the NHS Organ Donor
OL,8,FRegister and to support heart valve
OL,9,Fdonation if a loved one dies in
OL,10,Fcircumstances where donation is
OL,11,Fpossible.
OL,13,FJackie Brander, head of operations for
OL,14,Ftissue donation at NHS Blood and
OL,15,FTransplant said heart valves can be
OL,16,Fespecially important for babies born
OL,17,Fwith genetic heart defects.
