OL,3,CPlea for heart valve donors after dip
OL,4,Cin donations
OL,6,F"We think there are several reasons
OL,7,Fwhy heart valve donation has
OL,8,Fdecreased. Organ and tissue donation
OL,9,Fas a whole has fallen ` last year, for
OL,10,Fexample there were 100 fewer organ
OL,11,Fdonors," she said.
OL,13,F"Also, since the pandemic, more people
OL,14,Fare dying at home or in the community,
OL,15,Fwhere heart valve donation is not
OL,16,Fpossible."We're investigating whether
OL,17,Fthere might be other reasons, but what
OL,18,Fwe really need is for more people to
OL,19,Fsupport donation - you will change and
OL,20,Fsave lives."
