OL,4,Cin donations
OL,6,FHeart valve replacements are needed
OL,7,Fwhen a person's heart valve is
OL,8,Fdamaged, diseased or defective.
OL,10,FPatients include adults, whose heart
OL,11,Fvalves can begin to narrow or leak,
OL,12,Fand for children with genetic heart
OL,13,Fdisorders.
OL,15,FPoppy Wilson, who had a heart valve
OL,16,Freplacement in June 2025 at Liverpool
OL,17,FHeart and Chest Hospital, said how
OL,18,Fgrateful she was to her donor's family.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
