OL,4,Cin donations
OL,6,FThe 21-year-old was born with
OL,7,Fcongenital heart disease and needed a
OL,8,Fvalve replacement after her own aortic
OL,9,Fheart valve became leaky and narrow.
OL,11,F"It was a gradual deterioration. I was
OL,12,Fincreasingly symptomatic and it became
OL,13,Fdifficult to climb stairs," she said.
OL,14,F"Without surgery, I would have gone
OL,15,Finto heart failure or suffered a
OL,16,Fcardiac arrest."
