OL,4,Cin donations
OL,6,FProfessor Attilio Lotto, a congenital
OL,7,Fcardiac surgeon from Liverpool, said:
OL,8,F"Every donated heart valve represents
OL,9,Fnot just a gift, but a second chance
OL,10,Fat life.
OL,12,F"While many people are familiar with
OL,13,Fthe idea of donating organs such as
OL,14,Fkidneys, liver, or lungs, fewer
OL,15,Frealise that donating heart valves and
OL,16,Ftissues after death can also transform
OL,17,Flives. "
